OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779876311
OL,3,CHeatwave declared in Jersey as islands
OL,4,Cswelter in record temperatures
OL,6,FBoth Jersey and Guernsey have recorded
OL,7,Ftheir highest-ever night-time
OL,8,Ftemperature for May, as conditions on
OL,9,FMonday night did not drop below 22.2
OL,10,Fdegrees at Guernsey Airport and 21.6
OL,11,Fdegrees at Maison St Louis.
OL,13,FSt Peter Port and Alderney have seen
OL,14,Fcomparatively lower temperatures,
OL,15,Falthough still above average in the
OL,16,Fmid to high 20s.
OL,18,FHerm is also sweltering under the
OL,19,Fheat, but temperatures are not
OL,20,Frecorded by Guernsey Met.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
