OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779876311
OL,3,CHeatwave declared in Jersey as islands
OL,4,Cswelter in record temperatures
OL,6,FTo put this into perspective, the
OL,7,Faverage temperature for May across the
OL,8,FChannel Islands is high single digits
OL,9,Fto mid-teens.
OL,11,FWhile many are heading out to enjoy
OL,12,Fthe sun, authorities are warning about
OL,13,Fthe risks to health and property.
OL,15,FJersey Fire and Rescue Service are
OL,16,Furging people to be alert to cold
OL,17,Fwater shock as the sea is so far below
OL,18,Fthe air temperature.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
