PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779876311
OL,3,CHeatwave declared in Jersey as islands
OL,4,Cswelter in record temperatures
OL,6,FA fire warning is also in place due to
OL,7,Fthe "extremely dry ground", with
OL,8,Feveryone asked to dispose of glass
OL,9,Fproperly and barbecue responsibly, as
OL,10,Fit can spark a blaze.
OL,12,FGovernments in Jersey and Guernsey
OL,13,Fhave both issued guidance about the
OL,14,Fhot weather, reminding people to drink
OL,15,Fplenty of water, apply suncream, seek
OL,16,Fshade and check on those who may be in
OL,17,Fat-risk groups.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
